        "collapsible_row_PRnaRQ": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "ONLINE CUSTOMER SERVICE (HA NOI)",
            "font_body": true,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></p><ul><li>Receive and advise customers on SEESON's online sales channels</li><li>Monitor and process online orders</li><li>Receive inquiries, assist in answering and resolving customer complaints</li><li>Perform other tasks as assigned by the supervisor/manager</li></ul><p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Female preferred, age: 18-21 years old</li><li>Currently studying at universities in Hanoi</li><li>Cheerful, enthusiastic, eager to learn personality</li><li>Good communication, problem-solving, and quick situational handling skills</li><li>Honest and responsible in work</li><li>Good conversational English</li></ul><p><strong>BENEFITS</strong></p><ul><li>Basic salary + sales commission</li><li>13th-month salary</li><li>Training & development opportunities</li><li>Young, dynamic work environment</li><li>Employee purchase discounts</li><li>Gifts for holidays such as Lunar New Year, International Women's Day, National Day, Mid-Autumn Festival, birthday, etc.</li><li>Annual team building</li></ul><p><strong>WORK LOCATION</strong></p><ul><li>19-21 Yen Ninh Alley, Ba Dinh District, Hanoi</li></ul><p><strong>WORKING HOURS</strong></p><ul><li>Shift work:</li><li>Morning shift: 8:30 AM - 1:00 PM</li><li>Afternoon shift: 1:00 PM - 5:30 PM</li><li>Evening shift: 5:30 PM - 10:00 PM</li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY</strong></p><ul><li>Interested candidates please send your CV to the email address: <a href=\"mailto:retail.hr@seeson.vn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mailto:retail.hr@seeson.vn\"><em>retail.hr@seeson.vn</em></a></li><li>Candidates who pass the resume screening round will be contacted for an interview.</li></ul><p><strong>Note:</strong></p><ul><li>Email subject should be: <em><strong>[ONLINE CS] - Full name</strong></em></li><li>CV must include a portrait photo taken within the last 6 months</li></ul><h3>PRODUCT QUALITY CONTROL (HANOI)</h3><p></p><ul><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul><p></p><ul><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul><p></p><ul><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul><p></p><ul><li></li></ul><p></p><ul><li></li><li></li></ul><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><ul><li></li><li></li></ul><p>2026<a href=\"https://www.seeson.vn/en\">SEESON</a></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.seeson.vn/en/pages/contact-us\">CONTACT</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.seeson.vn/en/pages/user-guide\">USER GUIDE</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.seeson.vn/en/pages/product-warranty\">POLICIES</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.seeson.vn/en/pages/hirings\">HIRINGS</a></li></ul><p>ENGMy WishlistSave things as you browseTap ♡ on any product. It lands here so you don't lose it.Saves stay through this session.<strong>Log in to keep them permanently.</strong><a href=\"https://www.seeson.vn/en/account\">Log in to save permanently</a>Keep browsing firstNo account?<a href=\"https://www.seeson.vn/en/account\">Sign up — it takes a minute</a>Don't lose your Collections!Login to save your favorites and access them whenever, wherever!Login to SaveShareWishlist<strong>0</strong>Saved For You<strong>1</strong>Saved for later<strong>0</strong></p>",
